&lt;h3&gt;Knowledge&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;K1&lt;/strong&gt; tool compensation for the differences in length between the tools assumed during programming and the tools to be used for actual machining.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;K2&lt;/strong&gt; tool data including geometric characteristics, composition and usage&lt;/p&gt;
