&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;S12&lt;/strong&gt; produce and maintain jigs and holding devices to ensure sufficient workpiece vacuum&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;S13&lt;/strong&gt; develop and modify furniture CAD drawings to suit CNC processes&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;S14 &lt;/strong&gt;read and interpret furniture specifications and drawings&lt;/p&gt;
